      "content": "i get the \"balance\" thing but if u actually had to choose, which way is the more responsible path? like if you have to pick one to be the main focus for a country to stay stable, is it better to be fiscally disciplined and pay down debt, or to make sure people are taken care of even if it means more borrowing?",
